reviews.title: Just Excellent
reviews.text: This brand new restaurant in Ridderkerk is a new hidden-gem. Both the food and service is excellent. Dining area's both in and outside are top quality and spacious for just the right amount of people. If you are looking to eat a top-quality steak or fish this is the place to be. Dishes are well taken care of and very well made. This restaurant offers nothing but high standard food.

articleContent.title: Your Trip Just Got a Little Sweeter

seoInfo.metaDescription: With service to more than 300 domestic and international destinations, Traverse City Cherry Capital Airport is your gateway to this sweet city and beyond. Only minutes from downtown, discover world-class wine tasting and breweries, seasonal festivals, and the majesty of Lake Michigan right outside its doors. Whether you’re just passing through or staying for a night or two, Grand Traverse County is a must-visit destination to add to your travel bucket list.
